FuncDef: The display fwm eth-trunk profile command displays the data table of an Eth-Trunk load balancing profile. The display fwm eth-trunk profile command displays the data table of an Eth-Trunk load balancing profile. This command is supported only on the CE6863H, CE6863H-K, CE6881H, CE6881H-K, CE6820H, CE6820H-K and CE6820S.

ParaDef.Info:
Specifies the ID of an Eth-Trunk interface.
The value is an integer that ranges from 0 to 1023.
